{"text": " Introducing Pangolin, built for the Sola Security Hackathon. Sola's pipeline scans your GitHub workflows daily, classifying findings and alerting your team. Our CLI pulls data from Sala MCP. The Regex engine scans 105 workflows in a tenth of a second, then GPT 5.5 goes deep, reasoning through attack chains. Six confirmed, zero false positives, 29 proof-of-concept files. The report shows severity breakdown, attack scenarios, and downloadable proof-of-concept files. Detection isn't enough. One command generates a fix and opens a GitHub pull request with full vulnerability context. Everything flows to Slack. Alerts, reports, fix notifications, a complete security loop. Pangolin, scan, analyze, fix, automatically.", "segments": [{"id": 0, "seek": 0, "start": 0.0, "end": 3.96, "text": " Introducing Pangolin, built for the Sola Security Hackathon.", "tokens": [50364, 27193, 2175, 49499, 31178, 11, 3094, 337, 264, 318, 4711, 11164, 35170, 18660, 13, 50614], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.22056626819428943, "compression_ratio": 1.4252873563218391, "no_speech_prob": 0.03251001238822937, "words": [{"word": " Introducing", "start": 0.0, "end": 0.9, "probability": 0.9194034934043884}, {"word": " Pangolin,", "start": 0.9, "end": 1.52, "probability": 0.9319969713687897}, {"word": " built", "start": 1.88, "end": 2.14, "probability": 0.8405472636222839}, {"word": " for", "start": 2.14, "end": 2.4, "probability": 0.9979031085968018}, {"word": " the", "start": 2.4, "end": 2.5, "probability": 0.995857298374176}, {"word": " Sola", "start": 2.5, "end": 2.82, "probability": 0.5621452629566193}, {"word": " Security", "start": 2.82, "end": 3.38, "probability": 0.6538694500923157}, {"word": " Hackathon.", "start": 3.38, "end": 3.96, "probability": 0.8913608193397522}]}, {"id": 1, "seek": 0, "start": 5.0200000000000005, "end": 8.04, "text": " Sola's pipeline scans your GitHub workflows daily,", "tokens": [50614, 318, 4711, 311, 15517, 35116, 428, 23331, 43461, 5212, 11, 507